namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::NetClient::onError

\brief set the callback function that will handle errors

This function will be called whenever a call to connect() fails. The function will be called with a single parameter, a string of the error message.

\param callback the error handling function for this connection

\return reference to itself for call chaining

\code
    myClient.onError( function(msg) {
        console.log("Connection failed: "+msg);
    }
\endcode


\sa connect

**/ }